name: RocketJump (BibiClover)
description:
W,A,S,D or Arrow keys to move.

Space or right control to Jump.

Mouse to aim and fire.

Numbers keys 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9,0 set sensitivity.

1 being the lowest and 0 being the highest.

You can also use "-" to make the sensitivity go down and "=" to make it go up.

Made for N8Jam
